<span></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">Функции</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">BIOS</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
<span></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">Функции загрузчика.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
<span></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">Назначение системных файлов ввода-вывода.</span>
