                <p class="_" style="text-align:justify;text-indent:0.2958in">
<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">в) программное обеспечение</span>
                </p>
                <p class="_" style="text-align:justify;text-indent:0.3743in">
<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">Операционная система</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">Windows</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'"></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">XP</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">.</span>
                </p>
                <p class="_" style="text-align:justify;text-indent:0.3743in">
<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">Пакет</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'"></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">офиса</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">: Microsoft Office Word, Microsoft Office Excel, Microsoft Office Access, Microsoft Office Publisher, Microsoft Office PowerPoint</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">или</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'"> (</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">программа</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'"></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">создания</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'"></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">видео</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">-</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">проектов</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">:Windows Movie Maker),</span>
                </p>
                <p class="_" style="text-align:justify;text-indent:0.3743in">
<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">Средства</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'"></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">работы</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'"></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">с</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'"></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">компьютерной</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'"></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">графикой</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">: Page Maker, Fine Reader, Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Flash.</span>
                </p>
                <p class="_" style="text-align:justify;text-indent:0.3743in">
<span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">Браузер</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman'">: Internet Explorer,</span>
